1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 23=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(I Remember Now)

4
00:00:54,320 --> 00:00:56,920
A new issue of Qingxin Daily
has just come out.

5
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:58,600
Have you seen it, Tower Master?

6
00:00:59,440 --> 00:01:00,920
It's very similar to ours,

7
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,640
except it publishes novels

8
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:05,280
instead of poetry.

9
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:09,400
I almost thought
you were the one behind it.

10
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:10,240
No.

11
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,480
What?

12
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:13,400
Someone copied my newspaper?

13
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:16,040
Which one?

14
00:01:20,040 --> 00:01:21,000
We don't know yet.

15
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:26,640
Why not write a few new poems

16
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:28,080
to attract more readers?

17
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:31,000
I don't have time to write poetry.

18
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:33,560
The bank is completely out of money,

19
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,720
and we still owe the people millions.

20
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:38,280
If you pay off
all those debts for me right now,

21
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:39,800
I'll write...

22
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:41,800
I'll write poems for you.

23
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:44,640
Since you're exhausted, Tower Master,

24
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,480
I can't bear to pressure you.

25
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,800
Please get some rest first.

26
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,280
Your Highness, we've just received word.

27
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,880
Wangshi Tower is completely empty,

28
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,160
and we found nothing

29
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,560
related to the Qingxin Daily.

30
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:20,440
Could I have guessed wrong?

31
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,880
Looks like Jiuzhu's side succeeded.

32
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:35,080
The docks can begin.

33
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,280
Tower Master,

34
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:39,160
what's the name of our new company?

35
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:42,040
Candy Maritime Trading Co., Ltd.

36
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,280
Right.

37
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,040
Once Zheng Yuanzhao's men have left,

38
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,880
move Zheng Yuanhe back to Wangshi Tower.

39
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:50,000
He shouldn't have the time

40
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,310
or the energy to launch another
surprise attack for a while.

41
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:53,000
Yes.

42
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:56,040
Look at the accounts
from the past few days.

43
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:58,240
Not a single one has made a profit.

44
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,480
What have you all been doing?

45
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:04,840
Your Highness,
it's not that we haven't tried.

46
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,760
No one's buying our goods.

47
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,440
The gauze,

48
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,760
crossbows,

49
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,800
iron plows, and furniture you're selling

50
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:16,880
were all designed
by the Tower Master herself.

51
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:18,600
How could no one want them?

52
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,640
Your Highness, you may not know this,

53
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:23,280
but a huge shipment of new tools

54
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,670
arrived through
the docks these past few days.

55
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:29,240
There are spinning machines,
curved plows, composite crossbows,

56
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,800
new-style desks,

57
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:33,160
and all kinds of things
we've never seen before.

58
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:35,440
They're better and cheaper.

59
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,160
Our products

60
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,880
can't compete with them.

61
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,480
Tower Master,

62
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:42,480
Yuanzhao's products
aren't selling anymore.

63
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,390
Have all the supply channels
been covered up?

64
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,600
Rest assured, Tower Master.

65
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,120
The brothers
have been extremely careful.

66
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:49,040
He won't be able to trace anything.

67
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:52,480
Where did those goods come from?

68
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:57,680
I heard
they were invented by a foreigner

69
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,560
and shipped through a trading company

70
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,000
called

71
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:04,040
Candy Maritime Trading Co., Ltd.

72
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,240
What?

73
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:08,080
We believe

74
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:11,040
it's a foreign trading company.

75
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,240
Zheng Yuanzhao,

76
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,200
you've got some nerve messing with me.

77
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,200
I'll make you pay back double.

78
00:04:20,280 --> 00:04:23,280
Just to be safe, we'll arrange for Jiuzhu
to leave the workshop tomorrow.

79
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:24,760
Yuanzhao is meticulous.

80
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,520
There's always a chance
he'll figure it out.

81
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,560
Besides the workshop,

82
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,300
we don't have
anywhere else to make them.

83
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,280
Your Highness,

84
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:33,040
this shop's paperwork
is in perfect order.

85
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:35,120
We found no issues
with any of the goods.

86
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:38,040
In my opinion,
they really are foreign products.

87
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:38,920
Nonsense!

88
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,400
Did you see the quality of those goods?

89
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,520
Every single one is exquisitely made.

90
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,640
They're a hundred times
better than what I have.

91
00:04:46,060 --> 00:04:48,260
If foreign nations truly
had this kind of craftsmanship,

92
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:50,670
they would've marched
to Great Yong's gates long ago.

93
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,320
Well...

94
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,640
And look at their marketing.

95
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,400
Excellent products,

96
00:04:58,800 --> 00:04:59,920
low prices,

97
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:02,640
and no way to trace their supply chain.

98
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,440
Everything's handled so cleanly.

99
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,760
Who else could pull this off

100
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,720
except you?

101
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:09,960
Could it be the Tower Master?

102
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:11,160
Jiang Shuo.

103
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:11,760
Here.

104
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,680
Take the official seal

105
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,800
and shut down the docks completely.

106
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,000
Cut off their supply.

107
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:19,840
Yes.

108
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,360
Wait.

109
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:24,720
Mobilize the Imperial Guards

110
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:27,280
and come with me
to raid Wangshi Tower and the workshop.

111
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:28,760
Maybe

112
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:31,120
we can catch them all in one sweep.

113
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:37,120
Jiuzhu, tell the brothers to pack up.

114
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,100
Someone's following us.

115
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,160
Is it Zheng Yuanzhao?

116
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:50,560
Let's go.

117
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:53,080
It's that Zheng Yuanzhao!

118
00:05:53,100 --> 00:05:54,850
If it comes to it,
we'll tear off the mask.

119
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:57,640
Tower Master,

120
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:58,880
only if you stay alive

121
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:00,760
will you have a chance
to negotiate with Zheng Yuanzhao.

122
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:03,920
Caiyuan, you...

123
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,440
I agree.

124
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,080
If you won't leave,

125
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,080
I'll kill you first,

126
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:10,720
then fight Yuanzhao to the death.

127
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,720
You bamboo...

128
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,120
Get out.

129
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:29,920
You said there were only
four possible endings for us.

130
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:31,560
So...

131
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,240
come back alive.

132
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,080
Jiuzhu.

133
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,160
Where's Qingqing?

134
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,360
Why aren't the two of them back yet?

135
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,720
Did they get away or not?

136
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:17,600
Wait.

137
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,880
Why are you here?

138
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:20,600
Did anyone see you come in?

139
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,480
Are you trying
to get me killed even faster?

140
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,600
No one saw me.

141
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,240
I snuck in.

142
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:29,520
Aren't you my master?

143
00:07:29,530 --> 00:07:30,790
Why haven't you come to see me?

144
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:32,480
Why would I come see you?

145
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,640
What's there to see?

146
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:35,240
This is all your fault.

147
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:37,040
You turned my bank into a complete mess.

148
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,560
Jiuzhu's still missing, dead or alive.

149
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,740
I'm buried in debt.

150
00:07:39,740 --> 00:07:40,830
I can't even run if I wanted to.

151
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:42,440
And you're still running around
causing trouble for me.

152
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,320
Now get back!

153
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,040
What are you doing?

154
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,520
I barely tapped you.

155
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,080
Don't fake it.

156
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:16,440
No need to thank me.

157
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:21,560
What are you doing?

158
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,120
When I was injured,

159
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,990
who was the one
who gave me the handkerchief?

160
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:29,320
You remembered?

161
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,600
Not really.

162
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:43,320
This thing...

163
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,480
It feels familiar somehow.

164
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:57,680
(I'm done for.)

165
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:59,480
(If he remembers I'm the Tower Master,)

166
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:01,590
(and the master
who's been making his life miserable...)

167
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:03,520
(I'll really be doomed.)

168
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:14,080
(Before he remembers everything,)

169
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:15,120
(should I knock him out?)

170
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:17,160
(Or...)

171
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:21,480
Qingqing!

172
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:22,880
The Crown Prince has arrived.

173
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:24,480
He summoned all of us.

174
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:34,760
Get inside.

175
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,840
If you want to live, stay hidden.

176
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,990
Don't come out, no matter what.

177
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:44,200
Showing up at a time like this

178
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,840
can't mean anything good.

179
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,890
Press this against
the blood vessel. It'll help.

180
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:06,760
Go see a physician right away.

181
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:08,800
No need to thank me.

182
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:12,920
Here.

183
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,520
There's a small bump.

184
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:35,240
You are my slave.

185
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,440
Li

186
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:50,680
Qing

187
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,480
qing.

188
00:11:02,980 --> 00:11:06,370
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

189
00:11:07,130 --> 00:11:10,510
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

190
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:13,020
♪Your smile♪

191
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:15,570
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

192
00:11:15,570 --> 00:11:19,250
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

193
00:11:19,710 --> 00:11:23,020
♪Yet I stand before you♪

194
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:27,590
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

195
00:11:28,010 --> 00:11:29,930
♪Though fate tries♪

196
00:11:29,930 --> 00:11:32,510
♪To make us pass each other by♪

197
00:11:32,730 --> 00:11:36,150
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

198
00:11:36,410 --> 00:11:38,040
♪Though time slips by♪

199
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:39,800
♪As day turns into night♪

200
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:44,340
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

201
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:47,140
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

202
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:48,930
♪Blessed by fate♪

203
00:11:48,930 --> 00:11:54,090
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

204
00:11:54,090 --> 00:11:56,530
♪Your smiling face♪

205
00:11:56,530 --> 00:11:59,370
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

206
00:11:59,370 --> 00:12:02,990
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

207
00:12:03,510 --> 00:12:06,970
♪And wander the world together♪

208
00:12:06,970 --> 00:12:08,310
♪Holding you close♪

209
00:12:08,310 --> 00:12:10,850
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

210
00:12:10,850 --> 00:12:13,170
♪Your tenderness♪

211
00:12:13,170 --> 00:12:16,030
♪Is the brightest moon♪

212
00:12:16,030 --> 00:12:19,730
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

213
00:12:20,250 --> 00:12:23,540
♪Our love will never fade away♪

214
00:12:23,540 --> 00:12:26,000
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

215
00:12:26,530 --> 00:12:30,780
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

216
00:12:40,260 --> 00:12:42,420
♪Your smiling face♪

217
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:45,210
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

218
